readable.content: A white dog wearing a christmas reindeer headband plays with a brown dog in the grass among some stuffed animals . A white dog wearing reindeer ears is next to a brown dog . A white dog with fake antlers on its head and a brown dog play together outdoors . The white dog next to the brown dog is wearing a christmas headband . Two dogs , one wearing christmas antlers , tussle on the grass .
